{
  "stem": "1316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was a-- a Zionist, and one was a leftist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a match between the representation of both the Jewish clubs with a Polish club, the Otwock Sport Club.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was taken by these friends from school on a Sabbath afternoon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't tell home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was the first time I attended a football match.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw all the youth, the free, secular youth, buying treatment-- drinks and so on-- on the Sabbath day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we had a teacher in the Polish school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everything was in Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A Jewish religion was taught by an old man in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He couldn't control us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then a young teacher arrived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this teacher was a leftist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a Yiddishist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He started to read us from the Yiddish literature.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there, I got interested in Yiddish literature.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what happened in 1936, when were-- we were in grade seven, there was a pogrom, [POLISH] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was after the death of Pilsudsky and a few years after the rise of Hitler, Poland became more under submitting to rulers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't, well, propagate pogroms, but economic boycott to push out, to force Jewish masses to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then there was this pogrom [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the central committee of the Jewish professional workers organizations, under the bund, proclaimed a half-a-day strike, a protest strike.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they-- they organized the strike that-- all the-- all the young people that organized the strike, they-- they broken in to the synagogue without permission, into the big shul, into the big [HEBREW], and there they held a protest strike.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And what happened, we and I and a friend of mines, a few friends, organized our class, grade seven.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
